h1. body

h2. Purpose

Sets the body of the request.

h2. Examples

{code}
new RequestBuilder().post {
    uri = "example.com"
    body = "Hello!"
}
{code}

h2. Description

Sets the body of the request. As a convenience, objects that are a @Map@ or a @List@ will be converted to a JSON string.

{note}
This property is only useful with certain HTTP methods, including PUT and POST.
{note}

{warning}
This property is ignored if the [form|Request Builder] property is used.
{warning}
